by a curse.

800
00:36:12,469 --> 00:36:13,936
She had a seizure.

801
00:36:14,004 --> 00:36:15,571
You don't know what
you're talking about.

802
00:36:15,639 --> 00:36:16,839
My husband is a doctor here.

803
00:36:16,907 --> 00:36:18,574
