823
00:37:16,533 --> 00:37:17,734
Oh...

824
00:37:24,875 --> 00:37:28,244
I wanted to tell you
that night at dinner.

825
00:37:28,312 --> 00:37:33,015
But we were having
such a nice time,

826
00:37:33,083 --> 00:37:34,984
And you were so happy,

827
00:37:35,052 --> 00:37:37,086
And i knew that when

828
00:37:37,154 --> 00:37:40,256
