never have that again.

829
00:37:40,324 --> 00:37:42,825
I can't believe this.

830
00:37:45,028 --> 00:37:46,929
And i know you,
sweetheart.

831
00:37:46,997 --> 00:37:49,165
I know you would
want to quit school

832
00:37:49,233 --> 00:37:51,768
And do everything
you could to take
care of me.

833
00:37:51,835 --> 00:37:53,870
To help me.

834
00:37:53,937 --> 00:37:55,338
But no one
can help me.

835
00:37:55,406 --> 00:37:59,575
And i needed you to
accept that and not
blame yourself.

836
00:38:01,211 --> 00:38:04,147
You do blame yourself.

837
00:38:04,214 --> 00:38:07,483
I hope now that you can
realize it's not your fault.

838
00:38:08,519 --> 00:38:10,653
So she lied.

839
00:38:17,094 --> 00:38:18,895
Oh, sweetheart,

840
