00:38:21,298 --> 00:38:22,732
Because...

842
00:38:24,034 --> 00:38:26,068
Because it's time
for us to go.

843
00:38:27,938 --> 00:38:30,006
We can go in there?

844
00:38:32,142 --> 00:38:33,876
We can be together?

845
00:38:33,944 --> 00:38:35,978
Yes, sweetheart.

846
00:38:36,046 --> 00:38:37,780
Forever.

847
00:38:41,051 --> 00:38:42,952
Thank you.

